NAME
  drone-cli - Drone tablet client

SYNOPSIS
  drone-cli <yes/no> <block_area>

DESCRIPTION
  This drone program will control the leash drone. The leash drone will scan a square block area attempting to leash any entity

  This program requires a Wireless Card

OPTIONS

  <monitor_messages>   Monitor status from drone. Yes|no 1|0
  <block_area>         Square block area. Ex 10

EXAMPLES
  drone-cli yes 5
  drone-cli 1 5
  drone-cli 1 unleash
  drone-cli no 10
  drone-cli 0 10
  drone-cli 0 unleash